{"id":"b529582b-93b6-42ce-a6b9-61d6c2e000ba","name":"Parasite || GRIMM","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 245, 64);\"><strong>╭──────────── ༺𓄃༻ ────────────╮</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 245, 64);\"><strong><em>Part 23 of my 'CRYPT INC' series...</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 245, 64);\"><strong>╰──────────── ༺𓄃༻ ────────────╯</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64);\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">► <strong>ɴᴀᴍᴇ:</strong> ʙx-113</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">► <strong>ꜱᴘᴇᴄɪᴇꜱ:</strong> ᴘᴀʀᴀꜱɪᴛᴇ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">► <strong>ᴛᴇᴍᴘᴇʀᴀᴍᴇɴᴛ:</strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 231, 97);\"><strong>ᴏᴘᴘᴏʀᴛᴜɴɪꜱᴛɪᴄ</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 231, 97);\"><em>ɢʀɪᴍᴍ ʟɪᴋᴇʟʏ ᴛᴏ ᴀᴛᴛᴀᴄᴋ ʜᴜᴍᴀɴꜱ ᴜɴᴅᴇʀ ꜰᴀᴠᴏᴜʀᴀʙʟᴇ ᴄɪʀᴄᴜᴍꜱᴛᴀɴᴄᴇꜱ...</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64);\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">A containment breach results in you being trapped and infested by a parasitic bioweapon known as BX-113.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">An internal timer has now started counting down until this organism completely mutates your human genome, forcing you to search for a way to remove the parasite before it is too late!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64);\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 186, 31);\"><em>This bot is part of a mini-series where User is infected by BX-113 and is trying to find ways to remove the parasite before they mutate into a Grimm.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64);\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 245, 64);\">A 'Halloween Special' series...</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OmXo4G0_RAxaDj9rJjbIL.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 245, 64);\"><strong>───────────── ༺𓄃༻ ─────────────</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 184, 30);\"><strong>◇ OTHER BOTS RELATED TO THE STORY ◇</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64);\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/0e66627c-573c-420f-88fb-218d0fb71d84_character-imp-grimm\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/quXTv3t0fdWS9cfUd7XTu.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cf270c64-14e3-4de3-98e9-f7e6d3b39e75_character-jersey-devil-grimm\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nlN386BedmqpqzOtZ-1W-.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/88e5d423-859f-4085-8c29-3d99093e3e29_character-ghoul-grimm\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/b9b9Oph7sk5LLr8zPqJhV.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4e9c09c6-11c4-4e4a-9b2f-822f7b16b653_character-banshee-grimm\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/f60Xe_yNyzGzLqFIfaKLQ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b899a84b-0872-443c-bac9-